            "pathId": 7955735229694245750,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エイシンフラッシュ",
            "enName": "Eishin Flash",
            "jpText": "……しかし、日本の天気予報精度は、\n高いと聞きます。",
            "enText": "…… However, I hear that the accuracy of \nweather forecasting in Japan is high.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
